Roamind OG Image - 1200x630px
================================

This is a placeholder for the OG image.

To create a real one:
1. Go to https://og-image.vercel.app
2. Select dark theme with cyan accents
3. Add text: "Roamind - Your AI Travel Companion"
4. Download as og-image.png
5. Place in public/ folder

Alternatively use Canva free tier:
- Create 1200x630px canvas
- Use #020810 background
- Add Roamind logo/name
- Export as PNG